description.translate:
Titania holds the title of the Fairy Queen, thou a self proclaimed name. Claimed after a everlasting war between light and darkness.
 Though intimidating I know Queen Titania likes to indulge herself, so a Honey Glazed ham would be a perfect gift, for the leader of the Golden Court. Don't you agree, darling?

description.text: That looks absolutely scrumptious! This should appease a Queen!
